    public class ObjectFunctionSetSpecificationImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements ObjectFunctionSetSpecification
    An implementation of the model object 'Object Function Set Specification'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Obj Type
    • Arch Vrsn
    • DCA Fn Set
    • OCA Fn Set
